message: [[WP:AES|←]]Created page with 'Office of Lord D. A. Reeves'

[[WP:AES|←]]Created page with 'Historian, researcher & geneologist.   My time is spent on research, linking memorials, merging duplicates and connecting the dots.  I take my heritage, 'graving' and documentation very seriously and most respectfully. Accuracy is of the most utmost importance to me, not who 'owns' a memorial.  My sources are ancestry documents, SS and death indexes, census records, birth and death certificates and the like, and trees that have valid document sources.'
